name: Aves Syndrome
description: we are addressed by the fact that humans will be afraid of things that are considered trivial, 5 years ago humans were made to panic about the issue of viruses originating from poultry, now with other things, my expression is shaky when I see the events at the end of this year, the world seems to have changed and many things have changed. eventually have to grow up and go away, being a testament to how weak we are.
